The paper discusses the use of Isolation Similarity in SVM, which is a machine learning algorithm, and its impact on density-based clustering. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with clustering algorithms, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) or cs.DB (Databases). The use of Isolation Similarity also involves similarity measures, which could place the paper in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CL (Computation and Language).
